'''NBA Slam''' is an Indian television show about [[National Basketball Association|NBA]] [[basketball]] on the [[Sony SIX]] channel.<ref name=nbaslam/> It showcases the abilities and on-court rivalry of two rival NBA star players through the eyes of two Indian celebrity fans. The first episode featured [[Bollywood]] actor and [[VJ (media personality)|VJ]] [[Rannvijay Singha]] and VJ [[Varun Sood (VJ)|Varun Sood]].<ref name=nbaslam/>
